{"tid":2146449,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"傳友邦安盛納「制裁」入不保事項","createTime":"2020-08-08T14:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T08:27:00.000Z","uid":5195,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c27741ebdbec428d5c65de30dddd8e92264ee9d4","tid":2146449,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T14:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QV_K83sq0YMtO04Egac83NUHhTg=/802x799/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K7YV2VOP3BAB5DUVS25L5KJCAQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQV_K83sq0YMtO04Egac83NUHhTg%3D%2F802x799%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK7YV2VOP3BAB5DUVS25L5KJCAQ.png&h=78ab45e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國公佈制裁11名中港官員，網傳AXA安盛已經更新保單條款，並向客戶發信指，新增一般不保條款「制裁責任限制及除外條款」，惟信件上未顯示所涉險種。本報正向AXA安盛查詢。<br />\n<br />\n條文提到若涉及的任何賠償款項使保險公司受到聯合國決議的任何制裁、禁令或限制、或遭受歐盟、英國或美國的貿易或經濟制裁，或違反歐盟、英國或美國的法律或法規；公司將不會提供任何保險，及承擔任何賠償責任。<br />\n<br />\n網傳友邦（1299）亦更新相關條款，並指若認為投保持有人會令公司面臨任何制裁、被禁止或限制，公司可隨時書面形式終止保單，但該份屬於旅遊保險保單。<br />\n<br />\n分析：料外資保險公司會跟隨<br />\n<br />\n有業界人士表示，目前暫時針對一般保險、財產險，過去有部份保險已將制裁納入不保事項，料外資保險公司會跟隨，未知影響是否會延至人壽保單。他續指，制裁條款非新事，在國際貨運保險相當常見，「啲貨去到受制裁國家出現問題都未必受保」。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，部份保險公司的旅遊保險已納入制裁為不保事項，安盛旅遊保單亦有類似條文，友邦旅遊保單早於去年12月已有類似的條款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200808/WMVGJAY3ZNAAJK3OGHILZTNWKM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200808%2FWMVGJAY3ZNAAJK3OGHILZTNWKM%2F&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW4hk9ljSbOzVJb7ECUhiv3w%3D&h=449bfdce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200808%2FWMVGJAY3ZNAAJK3OGHILZTNWKM%2F&h=f9380a29\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200808/WMVGJAY3ZNAAJK3OGHILZTNWKM/</a>"},{"pid":"91e06c1ef8e96aee50c1a9ae3ec46fc53df8b099","tid":2146449,"uid":310700,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T14:49:26.000Z","msg":"國安法呢？？？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8bc7e2042db6dcc5d6dc7377cec9fd6f621aa5","tid":2146449,"uid":54622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T14:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a5d07e75041cbb69f32b6e8d14ad868515056e","tid":2146449,"uid":346701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T15:00:27.000Z","msg":"12大盜保單可以CUT咗佢啦，交黎都無咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97427cd00b918a7f3201849c7a6700b44410bf94","tid":2146449,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T15:15:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國公佈制裁11名中港官員，網傳AXA安盛已經更新保單條款，並向客戶發信指，新增一般不保條款「制裁責任限制及除外條款」，惟信件上未顯示所涉險種。本報正向AXA安盛查詢。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n險種梗係<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">ALL</span></span></strong>啦<br />\n<br />\n妓者究竟有無腦？"},{"pid":"c10fe784e35fc95f88d5e6a0e1ddc704dc8f3fbb","tid":2146449,"uid":101756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T15:17:20.000Z","msg":"強強老婆果間呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dffacb69eb7d5ac93d08bc3963b495836783de6","tid":2146449,"uid":37596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T15:17:32.00